The paper deals with the problem of generating posters from scientific papers, which involves layout and graphical composition. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) or Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper utilizes graphical models, which is a common technique in Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves learning from data, which is a common theme in Machine Learning (cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.GR and cs.CV, followed by cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.LG.
